responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "5EA186E74557FA5345F55CB2BE5B74AF", "I thank you, foolish Verran. Corruption is often unseen and its acrid stench never smelt by mortals, but I find it. I see it. I smell it. I hear it. I use it. It becomes the heart of my destruction.")
name: MIDD_0017_CTR_TheCryptmonger_14
